{"tid":874551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發有圖]今日present緊個陣走撚左出班房","createTime":"2018-10-24T09:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T09:32:50.000Z","uid":211452,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5f5ee9959608880ef6a8154515ecd3cced771017","tid":874551,"uid":211452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T09:27:03.000Z","msg":"話說今日present ，成team人夾好著返套西裝，加埋通宵準備，諗住掂過碌蔗可以爆4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\npresent個陣，坐前排D同學係咁笑，我即刻淆一淆睇睇份稿有咩問題，但咩問題都冇。如是者就繼續pre la，點知班同學越笑越大聲，我跟住同學視線望落去。<br />\n<br />\n仆街!成地Oreo碎... <br />\n再望真D，原來係groupmate個鞋底碎曬<br />\n唔知係唔係前排D同學笑得太大聲<br />\n懷疑groupmate惱羞成怒，present緊個陣爆seed講左句屌你老母，係前門衝左出班房，剩返個鞋碎係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班靜曬，miss呆左，我都唔知點算好，坐前排笑最大聲果個嚇到O曬<br />\n三秒之後，個groupmate係後門入返黎，坐返自己位。<br />\n原來佢翻翻去換鞋，之後又走翻出黎，好怒咁踢左下堆鞋碎，然後死死氣咁執翻啲鞋碎入垃圾桶。<br />\n<br />\n落堂之後條友即刻衝走左，全班人走出去逐個逐個影塊地，睇翻原來黑到仆街<br />\n<br />\n準備左咁耐既Project，今次實爛Grad啦唉<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/164403_adc04c5f667936a82a78f25d0fe346a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F164403_adc04c5f667936a82a78f25d0fe346a3.jpg&h=87103003&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/164405_9c82f0f47c90339d7399893f6e31012b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F164405_9c82f0f47c90339d7399893f6e31012b.jpg&h=88d383d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"673d8b4032668d4ffc5c04fd46e3a3e081329790","tid":874551,"uid":77478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T09:28:10.000Z","msg":"你悶唔撚悶"},{"pid":"5e76cf8e7be107e9f7298ca4cbe2e95b0deb4cf0","tid":874551,"uid":59151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy